{{Infobox journal | title = Topology and Its Applications | cover = Topology and its Applications.gif | formernames = General Topology and Its Applications | abbreviation = Topol. Its Appl.
| mathscinet = Topology Appl. | discipline = [[Topology]] | editor = {{nowrap|1=[[Jan van Mill]],}} {{nowrap|1=[[Jerry Vaughan]]}} | publisher = [[Elsevier]] | frequency = 18/year | history = 1971&ndash;present | impact = 0.377 | impact-year = 2016 | url = http://www.elsevier.com/wps/find/journaldescription.cws_home/505624/description#description | link1 = http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/journal/01668641 | link1-name = Online access (''Topol. Its Appl.'') | link2 = http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/journal/0016660X | link2-name = Online archive (''Gen. Topol. Its Appl.'') | ISSN = 0166-8641 | eISSN = 1879-3207 | CODEN = TIAPD9 | LCCN = 80649265 | OCLC = 5843055 }} '''''Topology and Its Applications''''' is a [[peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[mathematics journal]] publishing research on [[topology]]. It was established in 1971 as ''General Topology and Its Applications'' ({{ISSN|0016-660X}}), and renamed to its current title in 1980. The journal currently publishes 18 issues each year in one volume. It is indexed by [[Scopus]], [[Mathematical Reviews]], and [[Zentralblatt MATH]]. Its 2004&ndash;2008 [[Mathematical Reviews#Mathematical Citation Quotient|MCQ]] was&nbsp;0.38 and its 2016 [[impact factor]] was 0.377.<ref name=WoS>{{cite book |year=2017 |chapter=Topology and its Applications |title=2016 [[Journal Citation Reports]] |publisher=[[Thomson Reuters]] |edition=Science |series=[[Web of Science]] |postscript=.}}</ref>
